Kod mene je 4:17.

595
00:58:01,690 --> 00:58:02,649
4:20.

596
00:58:02,858 --> 00:58:03,775
4:24.

597
00:58:04,151 --> 00:58:05,986
Podesimo ih na 4:30.

598
00:58:10,115 --> 00:58:13,327
Trebalo bi da imamo sat do
zore. Koliko ti vremena treba?

599
00:58:14,912 --> 00:58:16,830
Biću spreman do 5 sati.

600
