654
01:19:06,038 --> 01:19:07,164
Kako je on?

655
01:19:07,623 --> 01:19:09,791
Nikad neće stići do granice.

656
01:19:10,083 --> 01:19:11,043
Niko od vas.

657
01:19:13,170 --> 01:19:14,880
Nemate šanse.

658
01:19:15,130 --> 01:19:16,673
Nikada niste.

659
01:19:17,591 --> 01:19:19,051
Mi znamo sve.

660
01:19:19,259 --> 01:19:21,094
